fields.description: List of content types on which compression applies. The value should be a valid MIME type.
fields.name: ContentTypesToCompress

fields.description: Indicates whether content compression is enabled on AzureFrontDoor. Default value is false. If compression is enabled, content will be served as compressed if user requests for a compressed version. Content won't be compressed on AzureFrontDoor when requested content is smaller than 1 byte or larger than 1 MB.
fields.name: IsCompressionEnabled
